                ancient Greek term "gymnasium". They are commonly found in athletic and fitness centres, and as activity
                and learning spaces in educational institutions. "Gym" is also slang for "fitness centre", which is
                often an area for indoor recreation. A "gym" may include or describe adjacent open air areas as well. In
                Western countries, "gyms" (or pl: gymnasia") often describe places with indoor or outdoor courts for
