                increased energy in the long run!

                “A lot of times when people are fatigued, the last thing they want to do is exercise,” says researcher
                Patrick O’Connor, PhD, in a news release. “But if you’re physically inactive and fatigued, being just a
                bit more active will help,” says O’Connor.</li>
